column5: Nice going boys, looks like a great time..
Thanks Alot guys we had a great time.
More sweet eyes.  Nice shooting boys.
JUST SO EVERYONE KNOWS LOL IF SOMEONE DID NOT SCREW UP( NO NAME )  WE WOULD HAVE BEEN 14 FOR 14. AND THE ONE THAT GOT AWAY AT THE BOAT WAS ONE OF THE ONES WE LOOK FOR ALL SEASON IN THE 14 LB RANGE
Wow...the pics just kept coming.  Nice job guys!!  dk
AWESOME!  WTG on the 'eyes!  I'll just have to keep dreaming about them until I get another chance to get out!
Only thing I could see wrong with the pics is the hat yer wearing congratz on the great day out boyz
That's it Fishhunter no shirt no leather jacket LOL

Hey Lloyd...was it something we said....didn't do that for us out there braving that 40 gusting 69 crap you took us fishing in on Friday... for 10 back pounding hours ! LOL  Great stuff none the less...good to see you squeezed a great day in between fronts.
Oh and the hat that's my buddy and I hate the wings too

LOL YA IT WAS A LONG WET AND WINDY DAY I'M SORRY THAT THE FISHING WAS NOT BETTER BUT I HAVE MADE IT A POINT TO MAKE SURE I KEEP A DAY OPEN FOR YOU TWO NEXT YEAR ON THE HOUSE. I REALY ENJOYED FISHING WITH YOU BOTH AND THINK WE WILL TRY A DAY OF SALMON AND TROUT IN OUR SHORTS AND T-SHIRT AND NOT IN SUB ZERO WEATHER LOL WAYNE DROP ME A LINE AND LETS TRY AND HOOK UP THIS WINTER
wowzer
Great job    fishing boys!!! Those are amazing.
I guess lake X is producing some nice eyes this fall. Nice pics.
You da man Lloyd !

Myself and one of my best fishing buddys joined FishHunter on the U&ME boat for the BEST fishing I have ever had.  First fish of the Mornin   then this badboy   Nice size eye   Then a little smaller but still good size   Another one    This one also beauty I should of had a pic in between there of the biggest fish of the day but it slipped off the netDAMMM ITT   Another one!   Always nice when you get a double Header   and another    and another    So in total we went 13 for 14 with the biggest fish of that day getting of at the net which was my fault. We had so much fun and lucked out with the waether it was a gorgeous day. All Fish we caught were anywhere from 6lbs to the biggest at 12 lbs I am super glad we could tag along Thanks Fishhunter you da Man!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Congrats, some great-looking 'eyes!  Were you at the Quinte g2g?  Mike
Your most welcome!!  Always nice to take OFC boys out for a day of eye hunting
wow nice eyez

I rarely find fish that size, maybe in the 8 lb. range, but that is the reality of where I fish. BOQ is a much different place, seen pics and videos of fishing there, size wise, its foreign to me. Not that I do not like the size of the fish I catch, but would dearly love to tangle with some that size.  Good going Gnoddy, and thanks for the report.
nice fish guys they look tasty uuuummmmm    jordan
Great report and pics!!! Was this at Lake X? or another lake?
Great catch!  Congrats!  Whopper
I can't believe the size of these eyes that people are posting.  Nice fish
very nice report and awsome pics i was there too and went 6for9 by myself for 2 days so i think i did well too,wtg
Congrats, those are some huge walleye.
What a haul, great pics of the walleye, you guy's will be telling great stories of this day for years. WTG.
Very nice report.  Thanks for posting. Almost makes me want to go myself.  Almost!
OOPS I FORGOT ONE SORRY GUYS
Great outing guys.  Congrats to you on your awesome day fishing them eyes.

Great haul guys! Looks like from a couple of recent posts that the bruisers are still east of the Ferry. What lures and colours were working for you? Sounds like purple and white were good choices but just wondering if you noticed the same or different.
amazing is all I can say
AWESOME! Congrats guys!  Again, always nice to see OFC'ers getting together!  Thanks for the post!  UF
real beauties!
....In a word...."Dang" !

geez missed my oppurtunity today was supposed to go with carp and my damn power went out in my house sometime through the night!!!Alarm clock didnt go off %$&^!Anyways beauty fish guys and nice drift sack gotta really slow it down for the eyes right now....
Nice haul!
Whoa, those are some chunky eyes, man........kudos.
Nice haul boys, congrats.
Beauty, was a GOOD DAY...
